Another interesting fact I got from a mother's magazine---research on women who go through periods wanting divorce show that if they stick it out for at least 5 years they report being happier in the end!! Also most who divorce say it was harder than they thought on themselves and the kids and they should have tried harder. Sure, some folks should divorce, but I'm against it too--especially for the children.<br>
